com.pgmacdesign.pgmactips.mapzen

Class MapzenAPICalls

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pgmacdesign.pgmactips.mapzen.MapzenAPICalls

  • public class MapzenAPICalls
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a Rest API to interface with the Mapzen back-end. Calls can be made here to return lists MapzenPOJO objects MapzenPOJO, which contain location data. This utilizes MapzenInterface and RetrofitClient for calls Mapzen Documentation - https://mapzen.com/documentation/search/reverse/ Created by pmacdowell on 2017-02-17.

        Query the map within a certain boundary
        Parameters:
        query - Query to search
        localizedLatitude - Can be null. If not null, will localize to said lat
        localizedLongitude - Can be null. If not null, will localize to said lng
        minLat - Minimum latitude. If null, it will omit the other boundaries
